{
  "work_slug": "the-maltese-falcon-by-dashiell-hammett",
  "work_title": "Maltese Falcon, Original Serialized Version",
  "work_author": "Dashiell Hammett",
  "audio_file": "audio-09",
  "audio_url": "https://archive.org/download/maltesefalcon_2511_librivox/maltesefalcon_09_hammett.mp3",
  "chapter_title": "Chapter 9 - The Liar",
  "reader_name": "Mark Nelson",
  "page_num": 4,
  "page_total": 4,
  "page_start_sec": 742.98,
  "page_end_sec": 938.46,
  "para_gap_threshold": 0.742,
  "segments": [
    {
      "start": 742.98,
      "end": 744.86,
      "text": "So we did exactly that"
    },
    {
      "start": 744.86,
      "end": 745.62,
      "text": "to him first."
    },
    {
      "start": 746.72,
      "end": 749.44,
      "text": "But then I wasn't any better off than I had been before,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 749.74,
      "end": 751.34,
      "text": "because Floyd hadn't any"
    },
    {
      "start": 751.4,
      "end": 753.1,
      "text": "intention at all to pay me the seven"
    },
    {
      "start": 753.1,
      "end": 755.02,
      "text": "hundred and fifty pounds he had promised me."
    },
    {
      "start": 756.24,
      "end": 756.8,
      "text": "I learned that",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 756.8,
      "end": 757.9,
      "text": "as soon as we got here."
    },
    {
      "start": 758.5,
      "end": 760.34,
      "text": "He said we would go to New York,"
    },
    {
      "start": 760.48,
      "end": 762.72,
      "text": "where we would sell it and give me my share,"
    },
    {
      "start": 763.1,
      "end": 765.98,
      "text": "but I could see then that he wasn't telling the truth.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 767.424,
      "end": 769.46,
      "text": "Indignation had darkened her eyes to violet.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 770.58,
      "end": 772.52,
      "text": "\"'So that's why I came to you to get you",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 772.52,
      "end": 774.49,
      "text": "to help me to learn where the Falcon was.'"
    },
    {
      "start": 776.14,
      "end": 777.3,
      "text": "\"'And suppose you'd got it.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 777.42,
      "end": 778.32,
      "text": "What then?'"
    },
    {
      "start": 779.52,
      "end": 781.34,
      "text": "\"'Then I would have been in a position",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 781.34,
      "end": 782.7,
      "text": "to talk terms with Mr."
    },
    {
      "start": 782.82,
      "end": 783.74,
      "text": "Floyd Thursby.'"
    },
    {
      "start": 785.12,
      "end": 787.2,
      "text": "Spade squinted at her and suggested,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 788.224,
      "end": 789.76,
      "text": "\"'But you wouldn't have known where to take",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 789.76,
      "end": 791.48,
      "text": "it to get more money than he'd give you,"
    },
    {
      "start": 791.6,
      "end": 795.04,
      "text": "the larger sum that you knew he expected to sell it for?'"
    },
    {
      "start": 796.02,
      "end": 797.54,
      "text": "\"'I did not,' she said.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 798.816,
      "end": 801.4,
      "text": "Spade scowled at the ashes he had dumped on his plate.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 802.88,
      "end": 805.12,
      "text": "\"'What makes it worth all that money?' he demanded.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 805.82,
      "end": 806.94,
      "text": "\"'You must have some idea,"
    },
    {
      "start": 807.1,
      "end": 808.96,
      "text": "at least be able to make a guess.'"
    },
    {
      "start": 810.1,
      "end": 811.49,
      "text": "\"'I haven't the slightest idea.'",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 812.32,
      "end": 814.3,
      "text": "He directed his scowl at her.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 815.488,
      "end": 816.4,
      "text": "\"'What's it made of?'",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 817.44,
      "end": 818.68,
      "text": "\"'Porcelain or black stone.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 819.3,
      "end": 819.98,
      "text": "I don't know."
    },
    {
      "start": 820.32,
      "end": 821.38,
      "text": "I've never touched it."
    },
    {
      "start": 821.63,
      "end": 823.94,
      "text": "I've only seen it once for a few minutes."
    },
    {
      "start": 824.91,
      "end": 827.1,
      "text": "Floyd showed it to me when we'd first got",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 827.2,
      "end": 827.84,
      "text": "hold of it.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 829.184,
      "end": 831.12,
      "text": "Spade mashed the remains of his cigarette in",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 831.12,
      "end": 833.28,
      "text": "his plate and made one draught of the coffee"
    },
    {
      "start": 833.28,
      "end": 834.26,
      "text": "and rum in his cup."
    },
    {
      "start": 835.3,
      "end": 836.44,
      "text": "His scowl had gone away.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 837.36,
      "end": 838.94,
      "text": "He wiped his lips with his napkin,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 839.1,
      "end": 839.56,
      "text": "dropped"
    },
    {
      "start": 839.66,
      "end": 840.64,
      "text": "it crumpled on the table,"
    },
    {
      "start": 840.76,
      "end": 841.86,
      "text": "and spoke casually,"
    },
    {
      "start": 843.42,
      "end": 844.64,
      "text": "\"'You are a liar.'",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 845.94,
      "end": 847.82,
      "text": "She got up and stood at the end of the table,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 847.98,
      "end": 849.78,
      "text": "looking down at him with dark,"
    },
    {
      "start": 849.86,
      "end": 850.5,
      "text": "abashed eyes"
    },
    {
      "start": 850.72,
      "end": 851.66,
      "text": "in a pinkening face."
    },
    {
      "start": 853.34,
      "end": 855.04,
      "text": "\"'I am a liar,' she said.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 855.58,
      "end": 856.84,
      "text": "\"'I've always been a liar.'"
    },
    {
      "start": 857.696,
      "end": 858.7,
      "text": "\"'Don't brag about it.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 859.04,
      "end": 859.94,
      "text": "It's childish.'"
    },
    {
      "start": 860.26,
      "end": 861.92,
      "text": "His voice was good-humoured."
    },
    {
      "start": 862.56,
      "end": 864.9,
      "text": "He came out from between table and bench."
    },
    {
      "start": 866.2,
      "end": 868.22,
      "text": "\"'Was there any truth at all in that yarn?'",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 869.38,
      "end": 870.12,
      "text": "She hung her head.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 870.944,
      "end": 872.74,
      "text": "Dampness glistened on her dark lashes.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 873.6,
      "end": 875.86,
      "text": "\"'Some,' she whispered.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 876.92,
      "end": 877.52,
      "text": "\"'How much?'",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 879.24,
      "end": 880.0,
      "text": "\"'Not—not very much.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 881.376,
      "end": 883.8,
      "text": "Spade put a hand under her chin and raised her head.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 884.22,
      "end": 886.36,
      "text": "He laughed into her wet eyes and"
    },
    {
      "start": 886.36,
      "end": 886.62,
      "text": "said,"
    },
    {
      "start": 887.712,
      "end": 889.14,
      "text": "\"'We've got all night before us.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 889.98,
      "end": 892.32,
      "text": "I'll put some more Bacardi into some more coffee and",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 892.384,
      "end": 893.26,
      "text": "we'll try again.'"
    },
    {
      "start": 894.46,
      "end": 895.5,
      "text": "Her eyelids drooped.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 896.18,
      "end": 896.64,
      "text": "\"'Oh,"
    },
    {
      "start": 896.64,
      "end": 899.58,
      "text": "I'm so tired,' she said tremulously."
    },
    {
      "start": 899.94,
      "end": 901.68,
      "text": "\"'So tired of it all."
    },
    {
      "start": 901.8,
      "end": 902.7,
      "text": "Of myself."
    },
    {
      "start": 903.12,
      "end": 903.88,
      "text": "Of lying."
    },
    {
      "start": 904.08,
      "end": 905.18,
      "text": "Of thinking up lies."
    },
    {
      "start": 905.5,
      "end": 908.14,
      "text": "Of not knowing what is a lie and what is the truth."
    },
    {
      "start": 909.16,
      "end": 909.84,
      "text": "I wish I—'",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 910.8,
      "end": 912.7,
      "text": "She put her hands up to Spade's cheeks,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 913.32,
      "end": 915.36,
      "text": "put her open mouth hard against his mouth,"
    },
    {
      "start": 915.56,
      "end": 917.42,
      "text": "her body flat against his body."
    },
    {
      "start": 918.56,
      "end": 920.02,
      "text": "Spade's arms went around her,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 920.08,
      "end": 921.14,
      "text": "holding her to him,"
    },
    {
      "start": 921.52,
      "end": 923.34,
      "text": "muscles bulging his blue sleeves,"
    },
    {
      "start": 923.58,
      "end": 925.34,
      "text": "a hand cradling her head,"
    },
    {
      "start": 925.48,
      "end": 927.96,
      "text": "its fingers half lost among red hair,"
    },
    {
      "start": 928.64,
      "end": 931.56,
      "text": "a hand moving groping fingers over her slim back."
    },
    {
      "start": 932.8,
      "end": 934.38,
      "text": "His eyes burned yellowly.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 937.16,
      "end": 938.1,
      "text": "End of chapter 9",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 938.38,
      "end": 938.46,
      "text": "Thank you."
    }
  ]
}